00:47:57,083 --> 00:48:00,920
<i>Bukti terakhir teoriku.</i>

464
00:48:04,007 --> 00:48:05,049
Di mana kau?

465
00:49:07,862 --> 00:49:08,780
Nam-hyeon,

466
00:49:09,322 --> 00:49:11,032
tak akan lama lagi.

467
00:51:02,994 --> 00:51:05,538
Seo-jeong! Yeong-mi!

468
00:51:07,415 --> 00:51:08,666
Sial!

