00:51:16,674 --> 00:51:20,678
Saat penentuan takdir telah datang,
Kang Pil-seong.

470
00:51:22,597 --> 00:51:24,015
Kang Pil-seong.

471
00:51:25,558 --> 00:51:29,312
Sudah saatnya mengakhiri
takdir pertemuan menjijikkan kita.

472
00:51:29,395 --> 00:51:30,355
Hwang Dae-du!

473
00:51:32,899 --> 00:51:37,320
Aku tak akan menyakiti mereka.

474
00:51:37,904 --> 00:51:39,739
